articles.title: Debate Night: The ‘On Politics’ Breakdown
articles.description: President Trump and Joe Biden essentially fought to a draw last night. That’s not what Mr. Trump needed.
articles.content:
For his part, Mr. Biden remained unfazed by the assault. He accused the president of trafficking in Russian disinformation and challenged him to release his taxes.
